# Copy to llm.env and adjust. Used by pydantic-settings (optional overrides).

# --- Local GGUF (default when not using --hosted)
# `pretend-models pull mistral|qwen` downloads the GGUF and writes MISTRAL_GGUF_PATH / QWEN_GGUF_PATH here.
# You may also set paths manually:
# MISTRAL_GGUF_PATH=/path/to/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.3-Q4_K_M.gguf
# QWEN_GGUF_PATH=/path/to/qwen2.5-7b-instruct-q4_k_m.gguf

# Llama.cpp generation (optional)
# N_CTX=32768
# LLM_MAX_TOKENS=8192
# N_GPU_LAYERS=0

# --- Ollama (--backend ollama); install optional extra: uv sync --extra ollama
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
# OLLAMA_MODEL=mistral

# --- Hosted OpenAI-compatible (--hosted)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
